    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting, emotion];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;inquisitor 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a thorny vine)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;up to one creature/level, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as <i>wrath</i>, except that you grant multiple creatures the bonuses against your designated foe. All subjects of shared <i>wrath</i> receive their bonuses against the same creature.</p>\n</div>\n",
